data.description: Yowzah! Five bedrooms and a full basement?  A stunning all brick custom built home with main floor primary bedroom suite and two-story great room with fireplace. You'll love the open concept eat-in kitchen and great room without giving up the formal dining room and private office.  PLUS, upstairs are four large bedrooms and two jack-n-jill bathrooms.  The lower level is nearly 2000 sq ft and just waiting for your special touch with two large windows and a full bath rough-in.  Three-car garage, screened porch and stamped concrete patio round out the wow.    Many, many updates to A/C ('22); sump pump & water heater ('19); roof, dishwasher and microwave ('16); furnace and fence ('13).
